Mahjong Score Calculator

What is it?
-----------

The Mahjong Score Calculator is for calculating the final scoring after a full game of mahjong. The point of this software is to fill the gap left by most other mahjong calculator software which only focus on calculating hand values.

The Latest Version
------------------

Details of the latest version can be found on the Mahjong Score Calculator project page under https://github.com/Tursake/MahjongScoreCalculator.

